vatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/57ae/ee35/229_normal.png?m=1448883313", "title": "English", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/en", "topics": 416, "footer": "", "header": "英语学习及使用问题讨论。", "title_alternative": "English", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/57ae/ee35/229_mini.png?m=1448883313", "stars": 395, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 229, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 775417, "username": "NeoWalnut", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/NeoWalnut", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_mini.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_normal.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_large.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_xlarge.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_xxlarge.png?m=1779853715", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/854e/dae9/775417_xxxlarge.png?m=1779853715", "created": 1763754764, "last_modified": 1779853715, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "unusualcat", "last_touched": 1779976651, "title": "英语学了几十年，还是听不懂说不出，大家都是怎么练听说的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216089", "created": 1779934930, "deleted": 0, "content": "平时工作中偶尔也会用到英语听说，所以一直挺想把英语好好补起来。\r\n\r\n但问题是，英语断断续续学了几十年，感觉还是停留在哑巴英语阶段。看一些简单的英文材料还凑合，但真到听的时候，经常听不全，反应不过来；轮到自己说，又很难组织句子，脑子里一片空白。\r\n\r\n英语 App 试了不少，没有一个有效的，多邻国、流利说、AI 陪练之类的都试过，但整体感觉效果都不太明显。有些是坚持不下去，有些是练完之后感觉没用，还有一些价格也不便宜。\r\n\r\n还上过一些公司的培训课，主要就是老师分享一段材料，然后分组尬聊，感觉这种方式只是在不断强化自己的蹩脚英语，也没啥用。\r\n\r\n大家都是咋练的啊？有啥切实有效的方法么？", "content_rendered": "<p>平时工作中偶尔也会用到英语听说，所以一直挺想把英语好好补起来。</p>\n<p>但问题是，英语断断续续学了几十年，感觉还是停留在哑巴英语阶段。看一些简单的英文材料还凑合，但真到听的时候，经常听不全，反应不过来；轮到自己说，又很难组织句子，脑子里一片空白。</p>\n<p>英语 App 试了不少，没有一个有效的，多邻国、流利说、AI 陪练之类的都试过，但整体感觉效果都不太明显。有些是坚持不下去，有些是练完之后感觉没用，还有一些价格也不便宜。</p>\n<p>还上过一些公司的培训课，主要就是老师分享一段材料，然后分组尬聊，感觉这种方式只是在不断强化自己的蹩脚英语，也没啥用。</p>\n<p>大家都是咋练的啊？有啥切实有效的方法么？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779941730, "replies": 65, "id": 1216089}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 3558, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 4440, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 538358, "username": "LittleSharkDaDa", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/LittleSharkDaDa", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8b44b86254ae61635cd7f4183b8c203?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8b44b86254ae61635cd7f4183b8c203?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8b44b86254ae61635cd7f4183b8c203?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1616116744, "last_modified": 1747193297, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "mylighting", "last_touched": 1779972766, "title": "是否存在港卡以外的其他选择？比如东南亚各国？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216059", "created": 1779930341, "deleted": 0, "content": "只有旅游签、本金 5 万以内、能够开国外券商投资、消费、没什么限制的卡，还有什么选择呢？", "content_rendered": "只有旅游签、本金 5 万以内、能够开国外券商投资、消费、没什么限制的卡，还有什么选择呢？", "last_modified": 1779933611, "replies": 59, "id": 1216059}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_large.png?m=1630643933", "name": "mbp", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_normal.png?m=1630643933", "title": "MacBook Pro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp", "topics": 9669, "footer": "", "header": "State-of-the-art processors. All-new graphics. Breakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps